name: 自由人生 (Free Life)
description: FreeLife, launched on November 13, 2025 by a Singapore-based team, is a BEP-20 token based on the BNB Chain, with a total supply of 1 billion FreeLife tokens. Launched through the Flap platform, the token allocation is as follows: 20% added to the PancakeSwap liquidity pool, and 80% for free market circulation. No tokens are reserved for the team, marketing, or development funds. There is no transaction tax; all buying and selling incurs only BNB Chain network gas fees. The token does not offer staking, lending, governance, or other on-chain functions; it exists solely as a community token. The token is traded on PancakeSwap, with liquidity provided by the community.
